# Chaos Pillars
Pillars of Chaos is a minigame based of Cubecraft Pillars of Fortune but with more chaos and for java and with configuration

# Features
- Spawns 10 players in a circle.
- Custom pillar types/blocks
- Custom floor types/blocks
- Easily configurable
- Automatically cleans up for next game
- Custom events for more chaos
- statistics option

---

# Commands

- `/startchaos` - Starts the Chaos Pillars game (requires OP)
- `/stopchaos` - Stops the current game and resets (requires OP)
- '/chaosreload' - Reloads config
- '/stats' - Displays stats
---

# Installation

Put the jar in your plugins folder
have paper 1.21.7
do /startchaos to start.

---

# Configuration

Configuration can be found in the plugin file and can be reloaded using /chaosreload.

---

